<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥubũka ạllãhumã yaj̊ʿalu .. ạl̊kulã kẖaẙr̊
 wajūduka lan̊ yubaṭãl̊ .. fāl̊kulũ kẖaẙr̊

[V2]
 2- ạản̊ta fī ạlḍĩyqi ạl̊manāṣu .. wamin̊ka lanā ạl̊kẖalạṣu
 ḥubũka hūa ạlạ̉sāsu .. fāl̊kulũ kẖaẙr̊

[V3]
 3- wāi̹n̊ kunãạ natāảlãm̊ .. fāl̊kulũ kẖaẙr̊
 fī ạl̊balạyā nataranãm̊ .. fāl̊kulũ kẖaẙr̊

[V4]
 4- ại̹dẖ̊ lanā ʿah̊du tẖabāti .. walanā kulũ ạl̊hibāti
 fabimaẘtiⁿ ạảẘ ḥayāẗi .. hā ạl̊kulũ kẖaẙr̊</lyrics>
<title>ḥbk ạllhm yjʿl</title>
</song>